==English==
===Noun===
'''bestiality'''
# status of lower [[animal]].
# animal-like [[instinct]] or [[behaviour]].
# [[mark]], trait, or [[emblem]] of a [[beast]].  "What's your bestiality?  (What's your mark?)"
# Sexual activity between a person and an animal.
# [[Bestial|bestial]] in [[nature]], savagery, [[inhumanity]], like (or akin to) an animal: "Man's bestiality to man"
# abstract entity similar to a [[beast]].

